  </alternatives>
 </disp-formula>where the rectangular prism with dimensions 0 ≤ 
 <italic>Z</italic> 
 <italic>≤</italic> 
 <italic>T</italic>, −X/2 ≤ 
 <italic>X(T)</italic> 
 <italic>≤</italic> X/2, −Y/2 ≤ 
 <italic>Y</italic>(
 <italic>T</italic>) ≤ Y/2, summation in the right-hand side of Eq. (
 <xref rid="Equ12" ref-type="">12</xref>) is carried out over an array of the XRDT 2D-projections, 
 <italic>n</italic> is the number of the inclined XRDT 2D-projections; the dimensionless thickness T is chosen to be equal to unity.
